.TH LEMONADE-ROUTER "1" "November 2025" "lemonade-router" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lemonade-router \- Request router for Lemonade LLM serving system
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lemonade-router
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
lemonade-router handles request routing and load balancing for the Lemonade
LLM serving system. It distributes requests across available LLM instances
for optimal performance.
.SH OPTIONS
Run \fBlemonade-router --help\fR for detailed usage information.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lemonade (1),
.BR lemonade-server (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Lemonade SDK developers
.SH REPORTING BUGS
Report bugs at: https://github.com/lemonade-sdk/lemonade/issues
